reviewText:
In general I like the Digi-View Cartoon Craze DVDs.  You usually get rare obscure cartoons in presentable, if not good, condition for generally a dollar.

But when it comes to Popeye, I must tell everyone that Warner Brothers is gotten the rights to restore the classic B&W and Color theatrical Popeyes from 35mm master negatives for a 2007 release.  So wait for that release.
